entry.title: Bundle - Oracal 631 Self Adhesive Matte Vinyl (88 colours)
entry.summary:
Vendor: ScriptDesigns
Type: Oracal Vinyl - 631 BUNDLE
Price: 89.95 - 161.55 (2 variants)

Buy a bundle, save 10%!  In this bundle, you get a sheet of every single color we offer in the Oracal 631 self adhesive non permanent matte vinyl.  This includes our 3 metallic colours (Gold, Silver, Copper) for a total of 89 beautiful colours.  

The bundle is available in 12"x12" and 12"x24" sheets.

entry.title: Oracal 631 - The White, Black and Metallic Tones
entry.summary:
Vendor: ScriptDesigns
Type:
Price: 1.10 - 132.00 (27 variants)

Oracal 631 is an ideal choice for temporary and short-term indoor graphics--especially in tradeshows, displays, museums and exhibitions. This 3-year film removes cleanly and easily for up to 2 years after application and has a matte surface that suppresses unwanted reflection.

When applying to walls, new paint should have cured for approximately 30 days. 

For more information on this line of products, please follow this link: 

http://www.orafol.com/gp/americas/en/products/plotter-films-product-details-10187/items/oracal-631-exhibition-cal

Although the colour samples shown here were created using the exact RBG formula, your screen may not reflect the exact color of vinyl.
